{
  "texts": [
    "Artificial Intelligence (AI) is reshaping almost every aspect of our social lives.",
    "Many of its far-ranging consequences are poorly understood and understudied.",
    "Its potential impacts on politics are no exception.",
    "There are myriad ways in which AI can change both autocracies and democracies.",
    "Although there is no conclusive evidence, many commentators suggest that these effects are already visible."
  ]
}